<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1451079-can-i-red-this-as-my-first-anne-rice-novel">Can I red this as my first Anne Rice novel and not be confused by characters in the book I dont know?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1451079'><a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F43805.Servant_of_the_Bones">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/1451079-can-i-red-this-as-my-first-anne-rice-novel">2 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/1451079-can-i-red-this-as-my-first-anne-rice-novel">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/45209230-susan"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1477014219i/45209230.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/45209230-susan">Susan</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
Yes the characters in this book do not appear in her other books.
</span>
</div>
