        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2926478076" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6579754690187195189">This book had it&apos;s problems, but it was a fast and easy read with an interesting premise. I really enjoyed the main character, and his struggle with his own identity. I also enjoyed all the historical bits, and I liked the author&apos;s take on the concept of spirits. The ending was somewhat predictable, but there were elements to it I didn&apos;t see coming. Overall, a fun read!</span>
  <span id="freeText6579754690187195189" style="display:none">This book had it's problems, but it was a fast and easy read with an interesting premise. I really enjoyed the main character, and his struggle with his own identity. I also enjoyed all the historical bits, and I liked the author's take on the concept of spirits. The ending was somewhat predictable, but there were elements to it I didn't see coming. Overall, a fun read!</span>
