        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3611314021" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16697433367533580002">I have a love/hate relationship with Anne Rice. I love her when she moves stories along. Her skills are wonderful and drive the characters and the situations beautifully. But sometimes she lapses into agonizingly long conversations to the point where the build up lasts so long the end gets anti-climatic.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


